@[simp]
theorem tensor_distrib_tmul (B₁ : bilin_form R M₁) (B₂ : bilin_form R M₂) (m₁ : M₁) (m₂ : M₂) (m₁' : M₁) (m₂' : M₂) :
    tensor_distrib («expr ⊗ₜ » B₁ B₂) («expr ⊗ₜ » m₁ m₂) («expr ⊗ₜ » m₁' m₂') = B₁ m₁ m₁' * B₂ m₂ m₂' :=
  rfl

@[simp]
theorem tensor_distrib_equiv_apply (B : tensor_product.infer (bilin_form R M₁) (bilin_form R M₂)) :
    tensor_distrib_equiv B = tensor_distrib B :=
  rfl
